# Sprint 001 — Video Engine Foundation

**Status**

Completed

**Period**

2026-06-16 → 2026-06-19

---

# Sprint Goal

Establish the technical foundation of the CopyStack Video Engine by building the first modular rendering architecture, introducing motion intelligence and preparing the project for future AI-driven video generation.

---

# Objectives

- Build the initial Video Engine architecture.
- Create the first rendering pipeline.
- Introduce timeline generation.
- Implement the Motion Decision Foundation.
- Integrate the first AI-assisted rendering components.
- Create the Motion Plugin System.

---

