# Architecture Decisions

During this sprint several important architectural principles were established.

- Modular architecture.
- Timeline-driven rendering.
- Motion abstraction.
- Plugin-based cinematic effects.
- AI-assisted planning before rendering.

These decisions became the foundation for every future Video Engine component.

---

