# Outcome

Sprint 001 transformed the project from an empty repository into a functional and extensible Video Engine architecture.

The resulting foundation enabled all subsequent development, including Cinematic Timeline, AI Directors, Story Intelligence and Research Center integration.

---

# Lessons Learned

Several key engineering principles emerged during this sprint.

- Architecture should remain modular.
- AI should produce structured decisions.
- Rendering should execute plans instead of making decisions.
- Motion behaviour should be implemented through reusable plugins.

These principles continued to guide later development.

---

# Next Sprint

Sprint 002 focuses on expanding cinematic intelligence through Timeline AI and Explainable AI, enabling richer planning and transparent AI decision-making.
